1) “download” basic.zip

2) unzip basic.zip

3) cat basic/Client.java  // “notice the package location”

4) mkdir ds/

4) mkdir ds/examples/

4) mkdir ds/examples/sockets/

4) mkdir ds/examples/sockets/basic

5) mv basic/* ds/examples/sockets/basic

6) javac ds/examples/sockets/basic/*.java

7) “abrir novo tab na shell”

tab original: 

8) java ds.examples.sockets.basic.Server localhost

tab novo:

9) java ds.examples.sockets.basic.Client localhost “port number given by server”